Code Range Category Example <code>ERR-AUTH-xxx</code> Authentication errors <code>ERR-AUTH-001</code>: Invalid OTP <code>ERR-CART-xxx</code> Cart errors <code>ERR-CART-001</code>: Product out of stock <code>ERR-CHK-xxx</code> Checkout errors <code>ERR-CHK-001</code>: Pincode not serviceable <code>ERR-PAY-xxx</code> Payment errors <code>ERR-PAY-001</code>: Payment failed <code>ERR-ORD-xxx</code> Order errors <code>ERR-ORD-001</code>: Order not found <code>ERR-SEL-xxx</code> Seller errors <code>ERR-SEL-001</code>: GSTIN already registered <code>ERR-PRD-xxx</code> Product errors <code>ERR-PRD-001</code>: Invalid HSN code <code>ERR-VAL-xxx</code> Validation errors <code>ERR-VAL-001</code>: Required field missing <p>All API error responses follow this structure: <pre><code>{
  "error": {
    "code": "ERR-CART-001",
    "message": "Product is out of stock",
    "details": {
      "product_id": "uuid",
      "available_quantity": 0
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></p>
